data.description: Great News for Prospective Buyers! This 3-bed, 2-bath gem in Fig Garden just got even more appealing - it now boasts a BRAND NEW roof, enhancing its durability and appeal. Furthermore, for those eager to transition into their new home without delay, the property is now vacant as the previous tenants have vacated, and we're geared up to provide a QUICK CLOSE!Experience the allure of granite countertops, plentiful kitchen cabinets, and pristine original hardwood floors that radiate elegance throughout the home. Enjoy the unique benefit of an isolated second master bedroom and bath, ensuring utmost privacy. For those who cherish outdoor moments, the expansive covered patio stands ready for gatherings and leisurely days.Nestled in the highly coveted Fig Garden neighborhood, this residence isn't just about aesthetics; its prime location ensures convenience with close proximity to premier shops, delightful dining spots, serene parks, and renowned schools. Seize this opportunity to own a home that's the epitome of style, functionality, and optimal location. Don't wait, as properties like this are a rare find!
